<section class="hero" role="banner">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <h1>
        설계부터 견적까지,<br />
        <span class="hero-light">한 번에 끝내세요</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-description">
        복잡한 CAD 없이 직관적인 3D 인터페이스로 데크를 설계하고,
        실시간으로 자재와 비용을 확인하세요.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="/app" class="btn btn-primary">무료로 시작하기</a>
        <a href="/features" class="btn btn-secondary">기능 둘러보기</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <svg class="hero-svg" viewBox="0 0 400 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <defs>
          <pattern id="grid" width="20" height="20" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <circle cx="1" cy="1" r="1" fill="var(--color-grid)" opacity="0.5"></circle>
          </pattern>
        </defs>
        <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#grid)" />
        <path class="hero-svg-path" d="M 80 80 L 240 80 L 320 160 L 320 320 L 160 320" stroke="var(--color-tech-cyan)" stroke-width="3" fill="none" />
        <path class="hero-svg-path" d="M 80 120 L 80 280 L 160 320" stroke="var(--color-tech-cyan)" stroke-width="3" fill="none" />
        <circle cx="80" cy="80" r="4" fill="var(--color-tech-blue)"></circle>
        <circle cx="240" cy="80" r="4" fill="var(--color-tech-blue)"></circle>
        <circle cx="320" cy="160" r="4" fill="var(--color-tech-blue)"></circle>
        <circle cx="160" cy="320" r="4" fill="var(--color-tech-blue)"></circle>
        <circle cx="80" cy="120" r="4" fill="var(--color-tech-blue)"></circle>
        <circle cx="80" cy="280" r="4" fill="var(--color-tech-blue)"></circle>
        <circle cx="320" cy="320" r="4" fill="var(--color-tech-blue)"></circle>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: calc(var(--section-spacing) + 40px) 0 var(--section-spacing);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-bg) 0%, var(--color-bg-secondary) 100%);
  }
  .hero-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--container-padding);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(0, 0.9fr);
    align-items: center;
    gap: 56px;
  }
  .hero-copy {
    text-align: left;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .hero-light {
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
  }
  .hero-description {
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .hero-visual {
    perspective: 1500px;
  }
  .hero-svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: rotateY(-20deg) rotateX(10deg) scale(0.9);
    animation: fadeInRotate 1.5s 0.5s ease-out forwards;
  }
  .hero-svg-path {
    stroke-dasharray: 1000;
    stroke-dashoffset: 1000;
    animation: draw 3s 1s ease-out forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInRotate {
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: rotateY(0) rotateX(0) scale(1);
    }
  }

  @keyframes draw {
    to {
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .hero-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .hero-copy {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero-cta {
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .hero-visual {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 80px 0 60px;
    }
    .hero-cta {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .hero-cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>